 the electronic\nenergy as a function of electronic number (including fractional numbers of\nelectrons) to provide a stringent assessment of self-interaction errors for\nthese complex anion systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 3 Mar 2018 19:18:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Mar 2019 16:15:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-20"}
