r protocol for a common image\nannotation task and deploy it in a test net of Ethereum. The experiment results\nshow the applicability of our protocol atop the existing real-world blockchain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 3 Mar 2018 22:42:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 12 May 2018 20:23:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 13 Jan 2019 05:17:25 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 17 Feb 2019 23:55:44 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 7 May 2020 17:53:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-08"}
